original_title: Umphrey's McGee: Picking Up The Tab
overview: TourGigs is proud to present Picking Up The Tab, the very best cuts from four nights and four massive shows performed by sonic giants Umphrey's McGee.  Eager Umphreaks packed the historic Tabernacle venue in Atlanta, Georgia as the band showcased their unique mastery of diverse sounds and styles.
title: Umphrey's McGee: Picking Up The Tab
